ore":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:44:52.000Z","msg":"加油，好好記住今日既事，努力儲錢，到時一有能力就搬走<br />\n記住唔好心軟"},{"pid":"2ceaf4d999a56cfe9448cc53c7f62001833ff75f","tid":1375460,"uid":274386,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:45:05.000Z","msg":"阿世伯咪就係得個講字，佢除左打撃你根本做唔到其他嘢去影響局面。有幾多個廢老真係唔收錢做嘢吖？我諗好少。<br />\n所以你自己一定要保重，因為你對我地好重要，多你一個可以影響好多。下次唔好為呢啲事受傷，無視佢嘅言論啦（堅難頂，我明）。保重身體去做重要嘢。早日康復。"},{"pid":"dff89bba89a2e1fdd0c3a3bafed68f15045da00a","tid":1375460,"uid":45007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:45:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d03133194678e6e17e47a702fe745094f650ec","tid":1375460,"uid":55851,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:49:45.000Z","msg":"記住呢個仇，第日搶間屋返嚟，再送佢上支那啲護老院"},{"pid":"25b762127c44d10cb72a7710ada1eb2d06ea756b","tid":1375460,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:50:31.000Z","msg":"死廢老唔值得留喺香港，一係就死，一係就返去支那"},{"pid":"8db649d82618e5033677c880b4d751897984810b","tid":1375460,"uid":67505,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:53:06.000Z","msg":"唔好搬<br />\n唔好做家務<br />\n唔好比家用<br />\n記住常備鎖匙<br />\n佢dum你啲野，你dum返佢啲野<br />\n搬出去不如用啲租嚟買gear"},{"pid":"a3d8332b457971e0d88c07b11ffc8656e2b76a71","tid":1375460,"uid":131122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a0ea8dd58b0e643d